And here are the exclusion criteria:

* "Any previous cardiac surgery under extracorporeal circulation";
* "Any previous perioperative cardiac arrest";
* "Any other cardiac disease (except heart failure with reduced ejection fraction)";
* "Any previous use of levosimendan";
* "Any other condition affecting the heart or circulation";
* "Any other abnormalities affecting the cardiac surgery (example: severe pulmonary hypertension, severe ascites)."
